headline: Communities received $9.3M from Alliant Energy in 2024
summary: MADISON, Wis., February 28, 2025--Alliant Energy and the company’s charitable foundation, along with the company’s employees and retirees, collectively contributed nearly $9.3 million and over 80,000 volunteer hours to various causes and nonprofits in 2024.
